msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid ""
"Single-node deployment completes both Prefill and Decode within the same "
"node, suitable for development, testing, and small-to-medium scale inference"
" scenarios. For the Qwen3-30B-A3B MoE model, Expert Parallelism (EP) is "
"required to distribute experts across NPUs."
msgstr ""
"单节点部署在同一节点内完成 Prefill 和 Decode，适用于开发、测试以及中小规模推理场景。对于 Qwen3-30B-A3B MoE "
"模型，需要使用专家并行（EP）将专家分布到多个 NPU 上。"

msgid ""
"> The following command is an example configuration. Adjust the parameters "
"based on your actual scenario."
msgstr "> 以下命令是示例配置。请根据您的实际场景调整参数。"

msgid "**Atlas 800I A2/A3:**"
msgstr "**Atlas 800I A2/A3：**"

msgid ""
"- `ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES`: must be set to the NPU chip IDs allocated to your environment (e.g., `0,1,2,3` for 4 chips).\n"
"    - `--port`: adjust to avoid conflicts with other services running on the same machine.\n"
"    - `--no-enable-prefix-caching`: disabled by default as prefix caching effectiveness for this model on Ascend NPUs has not been fully characterized. You can try enabling it to evaluate the cache hit rate for your workload.\n"
"    - `--quantization ascend`: required for W8A8 quantized models. Remove this parameter when using BF16 weights."
msgstr ""
"- `ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES`：必须设置为分配给您的环境的NPU芯片ID（例如，4个芯片设置为`0,1,2,3`）。\n"
"    - `--port`：调整以避免与同一台机器上运行的其他服务冲突。\n"
"    - `--no-enable-prefix-caching`：默认禁用，因为该模型在昇腾NPU上的前缀缓存效果尚未完全验证。您可以尝试启用它以评估工作负载的缓存命中率。\n"
"    - `--quantization ascend`：W8A8量化模型必需。使用BF16权重时请移除该参数。"

msgid "For parameter details, refer to:"
msgstr "参数详情请参考："

msgid ""
"- [vLLM CLI documentation](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/stable/cli/) — standard serve parameters (`--host`, `--port`, `--max-model-len`, etc.)\n"
"    - [Environment Variables](../../user_guide/configuration/env_vars.md) — Ascend-specific environment variables (`HCCL_*`, etc.)\n"
"    - [Additional Configuration](../../user_guide/configuration/additional_config.md) — `--additional-config` format and options"
msgstr ""
"- [vLLM CLI文档](https://docs.vllm.ai/en/stable/cli/) — 标准服务参数（`--host`、`--port`、`--max-model-len`等）\n"
"    - [环境变量](../../user_guide/configuration/env_vars.md) — 昇腾专用环境变量（`HCCL_*`等）\n"
"    - [附加配置](../../user_guide/configuration/additional_config.md) — `--additional-config`格式和选项"

